# Study02 - Single Layer Perceptron

## Overview
This study implements:
- Artificial Neuron
- Step Activation Function
- Single Layer Perceptron
- Binary Classification (AND gate)

## Key Concepts
- Weighted Sum (z = wx + b)
- Activation Function
- Perceptron Learning Rule
- Decision Boundary

## Visual Outputs
Saved in /Visuals:
- loss_plot.png
- decision_boundary.png

## Limitation
Perceptron cannot solve XOR (non-linear problem)

## Conclusion
This study demonstrates how a basic neural network learns and why deeper networks are needed.
